{"tid":1661229,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【叫人唔好糾纏7·21】政府短期內不會成立獨立調委會","createTime":"2019-10-18T03:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T03:27:19.000Z","uid":175314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa67c3c8a5f0be372284f92a27e8af47f7064727","tid":1661229,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/heDgsQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FheDgsQk.jpg&h=46ba94fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/2WyymX?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F2WyymX%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=fe964a99\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/2WyymX?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》引發連場示威衝突，警方執法問題惹爭議，示威者堅持要成立獨立調查委員會跟進。<span style=\"color: red;\">政務司司長張建宗今早(18日)在電台節目重申，港府無意在短期內成立獨立調查委員會，直至社會回復平靜為止</span>，而政府短期內將再舉行社區對話，聆聽社會的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對於他呼籲市民不要再糾纏於元朗7.21事件，張解釋是因爲監警會正調查近月的示威衝突，包括7.21事件，希望市民給予監警會時間和空間工作</span>，耐心等待監警會稍後發表的調查報告。他又指香港正處於非常困難的時刻，支持警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n東網網站 : <a href=\"https://on.cc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fon.cc%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=ca62b53d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://on.cc/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">反撚智，唔成立獨立調查委員會還黑警一個清白，咪只會一路亂局囉，成立調查委員會先係解藥之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢試下自己721俾白衫佬打兩嘢呀，屌佢老母涼薄到咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}